# ISR Baseline Soak — web-upload trigger file
# Upload this file via the web interface at ~2:30 into the soak run to exercise
# the flash-write / rmt_transmit code path (exposes ISR safety bug V5).
# The timeline intentionally starts LEDs and audio simultaneously at t=0 to
# stress the simultaneous-entry path (bug at t=0 listed in Phase 1 plan).

# time(ms)  freq(Hz)  duty(%)  brightness(%)  channel
0     8.0   50  80  0
0     8.0   50  80  1
5000  20.0  50  80  0
5000  20.0  50  80  1
10000 8.0   50  60  0
15000 20.0  50  60  1
20000 8.0   50  80  0
25000 20.0  50  80  1

# Audio commands (A prefix)
A0    binaural 200.0 8.0
A5000 binaural 200.0 20.0
A10000 sweep 200 400 5
A15000 binaural 200.0 8.0
